<exercise id="fs-id1172100577825">
<problem id="fs-id1172098513613">
<para id="fs-id1172098513615"><emphasis effect="italics">Haemophilus influenzae</emphasis> is a common cause of which of the following?</para>
<list id="fs-id1172100627708" list-type="enumerated" number-style="upper-alpha">
